		<title><![CDATA[Sample Page]]></title>
		<link>https://ccreadysites.cyberchimps.com/lifestylenew/?page_id=2</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 11 Jan 2023 09:41:36 +0000</pubDate>

		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>...or something like this:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="https://ccreadysites.cyberchimps.com/lifestylenew/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>

		<title><![CDATA[Era Of Fashion: 1983]]></title>
		<link>https://ccreadysites.cyberchimps.com/lifestylenew/2023/01/13/era-of-fashion/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 13 Jan 2023 07:23:02 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[lifestylenew]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://ccreadysites.cyberchimps.com/lifestylenew/?p=801</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Id dignissim libero felis quis suspendisse consequat ultricies. Aliquet ultrices fringilla gravida enim leo iaculis. Eu in aliquam duis aliquam accumsan.<br><br>Nibh scelerisque ut aliquam in. Et adipiscing dis nulla suspendisse ultricies mi volutpat nibh risus. Amet sed hendrerit sed id nisl pretium neque. Ultricies porta lacus fusce dis mauris turpis libero vel. Magna viverra lorem nibh potenti et. Adipiscing faucibus sit vitae ut vivamus rutrum. Maecenas purus convallis vitae feugiat.<br><br>Tellus a platea habitant est at faucibus purus orci convallis. Euismod urna sollicitudin lacus ultricies erat. Facilisis pellentesque lectus pretium quis ut. Quam etiam odio bibendum dolor malesuada pulvinar velit hac ultricies. Condimentum at ultrices nunc tristique sed ullamcorper eu fermentum. Morbi amet nec sit in velit a amet gravida eu. Lobortis adipiscing ut egestas justo ipsum sit. Quis tellus non pulvinar egestas. At pellentesque senectus vulputate vel viverra libero pretium.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":872,"sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full"><img src="https://ccreadysites.cyberchimps.com/lifestylenew/wp-content/uploads/sites/242/2023/01/Rectangle-150953-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-872" /></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Id dignissim libero felis quis suspendisse consequat ultricies. Aliquet ultrices fringilla gravida enim leo iaculis. Eu in aliquam duis aliquam accumsan.<br><br>Nibh scelerisque ut aliquam in. Et adipiscing dis nulla suspendisse ultricies mi volutpat nibh risus. Amet sed hendrerit sed id nisl pretium neque. Ultricies porta lacus fusce dis mauris turpis libero vel. Magna viverra lorem nibh potenti et. Adipiscing faucibus sit vitae ut vivamus rutrum. Maecenas purus convallis vitae feugiat.<br><br>Tellus a platea habitant est at faucibus purus orci convallis. Euismod urna sollicitudin lacus ultricies erat. Facilisis pellentesque lectus pretium quis ut. Quam etiam odio bibendum dolor malesuada pulvinar velit hac ultricies. Condimentum at ultrices nunc tristique sed ullamcorper eu fermentum. Morbi amet nec sit in velit a amet gravida eu. Lobortis adipiscing ut egestas justo ipsum sit. Quis tellus non pulvinar egestas. At pellentesque senectus vulputate vel viverra libero pretium.</p>

<p>Mandala is a crazy trend that has caught up on advertisements, T-shirts, mobile covers, apparels, furnishings, logos and more. Hop on to the design wagon with this mega deal. This huge bundle comprises&nbsp;<strong>1300+ Mandala Ornaments</strong>&nbsp;that can make every design beautiful, intricate and powerful!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Connect with yourself, free yourself, rebuild yourself and express yourself with these spiritual designs. Presenting a Magical Collection Of&nbsp;<strong>1300+ Mandalas For Creative Designs!</strong>&nbsp;Each design is available in 3 versions – Thin Lines, Thick Lines &amp; Colorful.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>You can use these designs for any project that you can imagine be it yoga, relaxation, meditation, spa projects, wood carving, tattoos, paper ornaments, patterns, t-shirts, mugs, phone cases, and the list goes on. You can color these designs in Illustrator, Photoshop, Corel Draw, Inkscape, or you can simply print them to color using pencils, crayons, markers, etc.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

					<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Completely Disable Comments]]></title>
		<link>https://ccreadysites.cyberchimps.com/lifestylenew/?post_type=wpcode&#038;p=4</link>
		<pubDate></pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[murtuzas]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://ccreadysites.cyberchimps.com/lifestylenew/?post_type=wpcode&#038;p=4</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[add_action('admin_init', function () {
    // Redirect any user trying to access comments page
    global $pagenow;
    
    if ($pagenow === 'edit-comments.php') {
        wp_safe_redirect(admin_url());
        exit;
    }

    // Remove comments metabox from dashboard
    remove_meta_box('dashboard_recent_comments', 'dashboard', 'normal');

    // Disable support for comments and trackbacks in post types
    foreach (get_post_types() as $post_type) {
        if (post_type_supports($post_type, 'comments')) {
            remove_post_type_support($post_type, 'comments');
            remove_post_type_support($post_type, 'trackbacks');
        }
    }
});

// Close comments on the front-end
add_filter('comments_open', '__return_false', 20, 2);
add_filter('pings_open', '__return_false', 20, 2);

// Hide existing comments
add_filter('comments_array', '__return_empty_array', 10, 2);

// Remove comments page in menu
add_action('admin_menu', function () {
    remove_menu_page('edit-comments.php');
});

// Remove comments links from admin bar
add_action('init', function () {
    if (is_admin_bar_showing()) {
        remove_action('admin_bar_menu', 'wp_admin_bar_comments_menu', 60);
    }
});]]></content:encoded>
